<li><a href='http://www.alan.com/2010/04/16/sec-takes-on-goldman-sachs-a-sea-change-or-a-big-fish-to-calm-waters/'>April 16, 2010: Alan Colmes Presents Liberaland - SEC Takes On Goldman Sachs &#8211; A Sea Change Or A Big Fish To Calm Waters? by William K. Wolfrum</a></li>
