<h2>My Advice about White Collar Crime</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<ul>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2010/07/my-life-as-white-collar-criminal.html'>My Life as a White-Collar Criminal</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2010/06/how-white-collar-criminals-exploit-your.html'>How White-Collar Criminals Exploit Your Vanity - Beware of Compliments</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2010/06/why-president-barack-obama-must-take.html'>Why President Barack Obama Must Take Steps to Significantly Increase Law Enforcement Resources to Combat White-Collar Crime</a></li>
