<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2010/05/bomb-found-in-new-york-citys-times.html'>Bomb Found in New York City's Times Square: A Warning from a Convicted Felon</a></li>
<li><a href='http://www.thehallofinfamy.org/blog/2009/12/crazy-eddie-inductee-talks-about-walls-of-false-integrity/'>Crazy Eddie inductee talks about walls of false integrity</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2009/06/memo-to-president-barack-obama-from.html'>Memo to President Barack Obama from a Convicted Felon: Be Prepared For an Unprecedented Onslaught of White Collar Crime</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2009/03/understanding-mind-of-bernie-madoff.html'>Understanding the Mind of Bernie Madoff</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/12/new-years-message-from-convicted-felon.html'>A New Year&#8217;s Message from a Convicted Felon: While you hope, criminals prey</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/12/is-there-really-more-white-collar-crime.html'>Is there really more white collar crime today? No.</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/11/advise-to-president-elect-barack-obama.html'>Advice to President-Elect Barack Obama about Combating White Collar Crime From a Convicted Felon</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2007/06/advice-about-trust-from-convicted-felon.html'>Advice about Trust from a Convicted Felon</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/10/why-white-collar-criminals-do-not-fear.html'>Why White Collar Criminals Do Not Fear Today's FBI</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/10/crisis-of-confidence-some-small-steps.html'>A Crisis of Confidence: Some Small Steps We Can Take Now</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/07/limiting-auditor-liability-is-plain.html'>Limiting Auditor Liability is Plain Dumb</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2008/05/warning-from-convicted-felon-dont-be.html'>Warning from a Convicted Felon: Don't Be Fooled by People Who Flaunt Their Integrity</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2007/10/warning-to-wall-street-analysts-from.html'>A Warning to Wall Street Analysts from a Convicted Felon</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2007/09/advice-from-convicted-felon-how.html'>Advice from a convicted felon: How the government investigates and prosecutes white collar criminal cases</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2006/12/art-of-spinning-how-to-identify.html'>The Art of Spinning: How to Identify Possible White Collar Criminals or at Least Unethical and Deceitful People Who You Should Avoid</a></li>
<li><a href='http://whitecollarfraud.blogspot.com/2006/12/managing-earnings-playing-numbers-game.html'>Managing Earnings: Playing the Numbers Game</a></li>
